# Why Uncarved?

## The name of this website has a specific meaning that derives from
Taoism

The Uncarved Block is a common English translation of a [5]Taoist
concept called "[6]pu". A block of wood that is not yet carved has no
set form, it is thus infinite in potential and free from desire.
